### Manual Configuration for Zed

To manually connect Zed to MCP Scooter:

1. Open your Zed settings (`settings.json`).
2. Add the following to the `mcp_servers` section:

```json
{
  "mcp_servers": {
    "mcp-scooter": {
      "url": "http://localhost:6277/profiles/{profile}/sse"
    }
  }
}
```
